visual_description.name: outdoor_garden_seating_with_white_flowers.jpg
visual_description.description: Blue and white wooden chairs, round tables on stone patio, lush greenery, white flowers in foreground. Natural light. Slight blur on foreground flowers, background in focus. Image not fake.
